outputs.output_descr: The overall goal of the project is to strengthen the financial sustainability of the protected area system and its legal foundation through elaborating legal/policy/regulatory changes, development of capacities needed to implement the financing plan and the field demonstration and testing of new financial tools and of new public/private partnerships.
